{"tid":2448046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紀念弗洛伊德之死歌曲《我無法呼吸》榮獲格萊美年度歌曲","createTime":"2021-03-15T15:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T22:14:02.000Z","uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"399903688a1903d13c59ea5c08f2ab7207977de2","tid":2448046,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:32:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IRZWiqBHYaY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIRZWiqBHYaY&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirD1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=da2f7d96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IRZWiqBHYaY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaOeGFx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaOeGFx.jpg&h=0fcd058c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地時間14日，在格萊美頒獎典禮上，歌手H.E.R.演唱的歌曲《我無法呼吸》被評為年度最佳歌曲。這首歌曲是為紀念遭白人警察跪壓身亡的美國非裔男子弗洛伊德之死而創作的，也是記錄全美各地&ldquo;黑人的命也是命&rdquo;抗議活動的一首歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該歌曲于2020年夏天發行，引用了弗洛伊德在去世前的最後一句話&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;我無法呼吸&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n領獎時，H.E.R.稱，從未想過自己的恐懼和痛苦會形成影響，並且帶來改變。<br />\n<br />\n她補充道，&ldquo;這就是我做音樂的原因&rdquo;，&ldquo;我非常非常感激&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"2544225b924c7e87f230d94bba533231ae46acae","tid":2448046,"uid":174945,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"黑血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14486fa73fbb0f7eeeffb3191f566e81968955e6","tid":2448046,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6802fc5e2e36ffa5a32c95823c4e64f600f78dc9","tid":2448046,"uid":19527,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"rep